        "checksum": "af203230da590da1e27302b7c2bdfd1f893d5cc4dd5db8d5847cb7f967668510_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-WuHZWR1w_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#727272;font-size:11pt;\">Our top pick of 2026</span></p>",
        "gg2SjuLyxqh_text": "<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16pt;\"><strong>#5 - Pixi Volume Mask</strong></span>",
        "gg594znBlKI_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">4,1/5,0</span></p>",
        "gg6nJGCmUaO_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>PROS:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">The bamboo cellulose sheet is eco-friendly and durable enough to prevent tearing during application. Delivers mild hydration at an affordable price point for daily masking. Works well for maintenance, but lacks the potency needed for visible anti-aging results in mature skin.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>CONS:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Surface-level hydration only. Results fade same day</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">No molecular weight specification (not deep penetration)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Generic anti-aging claims (not mature skin specific)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Lower essence amount than premium competitors</span></li></ul>",
        "gg8JhvIiech_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#727272;font-size:11pt;\">Our top pick of 2026</span></p>",
        "gg90nv4uWsO_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>PROS:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">You get a decent amount of essence that gives your skin a good level of hydration. Cheaply priced compared to premium options, easy to find online whenever you need it. Good for younger skin wanting temporary hydration boost, but not suitable for mature/sensitive skin or those seeking lasting results.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>CONS:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Skin irritation reports (burning, swelling, redness reviews)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Very easy to rip or tear - fragile hydrogel material</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Amazon counterfeit reports. Documented cases of severe skin damage from fakes</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Results fade within 1-2 days&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Generic formulation</span></li></ul>",
        "ggAMBZLFGX9_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">4,8/5,0</span></p>",
        "ggCEnspH8DV_text": "<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16pt;\"><strong>🏆 #1 - NIFORA Bio-Collagen Mask</strong></span>",
        "ggF7zofUAiP_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">3,5/5,0</span></p>",
        "ggFt0M9E7Ek_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>PROS:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">The accessible price point makes it reasonable for budget-conscious shoppers or those new to collagen masks. Generally well-tolerated by most users with minimal reports of irritation or adverse reactions. Provides basic hydration at the entry-level price, but the formula lacks the transformative results on aging skin.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>CONS:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Botanical collagen has larger molecular size&nbsp;(can't penetrate as deeply)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Results fade same day</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Standard sheet mask thickness</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Basic hydration only&nbsp;</span></li></ul>",
