        "ggkj_ZEq2qr_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">3,5/5,0</span></p>",
        "ggmHlssPvo4_text": "<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16pt;\"><strong>#2 - Biodance Collagen Mask</strong></span>",
        "ggmn1cHBd7B_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">3,8/5,0</span></p>",
        "ggnPZ0myiTZ_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>PROS:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">The only mask with&nbsp;<strong>ultra-low-molecular weight bio-collagen</strong> that actually penetrates deep into your skin. After just one use, you'll see&nbsp;<strong>lasting hydration, smoother fine lines, plumper skin, and a natural glow&nbsp;</strong>that gives you the confidence to go&nbsp;<strong>makeup-free.&nbsp;</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">Results last a&nbsp;<strong>full 7 days</strong> from just one weekly use. No need for nightly masking just to keep your glow. The generous 35g of essence covers your entire face without drying out halfway, and it's&nbsp;<strong>gentle enough for mature, sensitive skin that reacts to everything else.</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>In the sections down below, we even tested the mask on multiple women and the results shocked us!</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>CONS:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Slightly higher price than “viral” alternatives (but justified by the safe formula and long-lasting results)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Not as widely known (newer brand, but growing fast)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Limited stocks and sells out quickly due to rising demand and popularity (as of writing this)</span></li></ul>",
        "ggoT1-xHfTz_text": "<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16pt;\"><strong>#4 - Medicube Wrapping Mask</strong></span>",
        "ggtfeoKwn5L_label": "<p>Check availability</p>",
        "ggupzgxAIXF_text": "<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16pt;\"><strong>#4 - Medicube Wrapping Mask</strong></span>",
        "ggvEGqN4hNM_label": "<p>Check availability</p>",
        "ggvwoX5tw4l_label": "<p>Check availability</p>",
        "ggwEoqL9GgB_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>PROS:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Features a unique peel-off gel format that eliminates sheet tearing issues.The brush application is straightforward and allows for overnight wear. However, the peel-off process can irritate mature or sensitive skin, and the application technique requires practice to achieve even coverage and consistent results.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>CONS:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Allergic reaction reports (red, itchy face upon peeling)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Not suitable for sensitive skin</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Learning curve for application</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Can feel tight/uncomfortable</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Results temporary (1-2 days)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Higher price point&nbsp;</span></li></ul>",
