        "checksum": "d9b3261dd2b207ab24008cd9e3c21f5056653d394806180619532d5e53ab57ed_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-gFCAvZNj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/9_633ade6e-b416-4547-9ab3-3b208a677b30.png?v=1770023047",
        "gg0bG7Pm1Xr_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Now, I know what you're thinking:</span></p>",
        "gg14VmCgx1a_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/5_9f20ce43-9442-47bb-82b5-e224027ad420.png",
        "gg3e9vBylO3_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">We saw hydration and glow that lasted up to 7 days on all women. Smoothened fine lines &amp; wrinkles that made them look 5 years younger. Zero redness and irritation for women in their 40s, 50s, and even 60s. Finally, it gave them the confidence to step outside without makeup, making Nifora’s Bio-Collagen Mask our top recommendation for the best collagen mask!</span></p>",
        "gg3w55rCEsA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/8_923eb5a8-03e8-445a-926e-b16b3c3de0dc.png?v=1770023035",
        "gg4IaIhPEyj_text": "<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11px;\"><i><strong>\"This sounds great on paper, but does it actually work for someone like me?\"</strong></i></span>",
        "gg7SPReVmGa_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/1_211858f6-e560-4f91-8f84-ee4df264cfbc.png?v=1770022925",
        "gg8pFPuPEvD_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(254, 235, 219, 0);\">After</span></p>",
        "gg9xQayql1U_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">9 out of 10 participants reported visible improvement within 24 hours.</span></p>",
        "gg9yugKf4-K_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>“At this age I stopped believing in promises since I’ve tried it all and still nothing worked.</i></span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>But participating in this Nifora trial made me believe in skincare again because I’ve been looking softer and more plumpy since using it. And I love how it’s so gentle on my skin! No redness or irritation until now. My daughter even told me how I look more well-rested when she visited me for my birthday and it’s definitely because of this”</i></span></p>",
        "ggD6rX4AHCP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/7_a25362c6-2f3a-4597-9b1d-4180b8f35e37.png",
        "ggDRaLiMWQp_text": "<p>After we published this interview with Dr. Nicole Miller, Nifora has reached out to us with an exclusive offer. They're offering up to 75% off their Bio-Collagen Masks with free shipping and a 60-day satisfaction guarantee for Cosmetic Times readers.</p>",
        "ggDu9yC5_kP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_f8956509-d0d5-4244-a56b-b0c33f949c24.png",
        "ggFSkALjGGH_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">By day 2, all 10 showed measurable changes in skin hydration, texture, and plumpness and the results lasted until Day 7.</span></p>",
        "ggGJbonDA_1_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Conclusion</span></p>",
        "ggKDYWH4H7-_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/7_7034d4a2-63d5-4528-aba9-aa608bad2f52.png?v=1770023022",
        "ggQPK_a7MHw_text": "<span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Putting The Mask To The Test</span>",
        "ggRCRizUV0x_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Women with dull and dry skin. Visible dehydration and fine lines.</span></p>",
        "ggSEFBhDMwL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/206_4afda4b2-dd6e-46ef-8761-e76940258459.png",
        "ggTivP3seuL_text": "<p><strong>Each woman had different concerns:</strong></p>",
        "ggVwC5tFypr_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/9_d9697282-4a47-45c2-adef-783cc97097f5.png",
        "ggaTTE-hrKk_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_b2979c39-3a68-47b4-ba68-ab8411ca8fb7.png",
        "ggai_P8Ew19_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/10_ef9cb98c-5bbc-4768-ae64-c988bbfe7988.png",
        "ggazogF3U67_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:20px;\"><strong>Take advantage of this limited-time offer,&nbsp;and try Nifora’s Bio-Collagen Mask today!</strong></span></p>",
        "ggbnfKrir3R_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/10_71ad1068-98c7-4568-ab86-bf80693ac7b4.png?v=1770023058",
        "ggc3lJQbDoh_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/6_2a717f9b-3754-48fa-99c1-a6171b470181.png?v=1770023004",
        "ggcYIbrGci9_text": "<p>Here's what happened:</p>",
        "ggd5GbzxuL6_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>“I'm at that awkward stage where I'm too young for botox but too old for the products that worked in my 30s</i></span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>My skin just looked tired all the time even when I wasn't. So glad I tried Nifora’s bio-collagen mask because it gave me back that refreshed glow that I haven’t seen in years!! Been waking up to a faceI love seeing in the mirror!”</i></span></p>",
        "ggdeOJe_YNN_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:30px;\"><strong>Women who used Nifora's bio-collagen mask saw:</strong></span></p>",
        "ggdh5komFja_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_5c44752b-e1b8-4136-8689-ce07227d96eb.png",
        "ggePv6bV38k_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/207_bef2efd3-35ad-4726-978d-9626c1c19f34.png",
        "ggftsBAxLnH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/3_c0489748-9a25-4953-82d8-3345a55fdcc2.png?v=1770022955",
        "gghR1JuaRPx_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Transformed skin that's well-hydrated and younger-looking. Visible glow that isn't greasy or oily, and smoother skin that makes fine lines and wrinkles less visible.</span></p>",
        "ggiQJ3EREPy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/8_8752058d-1574-4024-a6ae-3d0ac5ebf443.png",
        "ggiid4EgvKt_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Nifora uses&nbsp;ultra-low molecular weight bio-collagen — small enough to actually penetrate into your skin's deeper layers and repair your moisture barrier from within.</span></p>",
        "ggjQL6kmXA9_text": "<p>Editor's note</p>",
        "ggjrWP0lztm_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/209_da174f50-1e8f-49a7-824c-ac86b538976f.png",
        "ggnzfdr-cOJ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/4_d9a8f04e-d01a-4ce5-be5d-fdbce8e9eadf.png?v=1770022972",
        "ggo8YCWHCgV_label": "<p>Check availability</p>",
        "ggorXxm6Xd8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/2_b1eb9507-7d21-4a36-a6c2-c5a619437470.png?v=1770022941",
        "ggp8GDur-MV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/4_a5bbe73f-09fb-4eef-b7b2-5d6beadb8709.png",
        "ggrGjRfc6r5_text": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Fine lines and jowl sagging that aged them beyond their years</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Waking up to sleep creases that stayed all day</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Dull and dry skin despite layers of moisturizers&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Tired of 10-step routines that ate up 30 minutes twice a day</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Sensitive skin that reacted to \"gentle\" products</span></li></ul>",
        "ggrkBiCcQdR_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Most collagen masks use molecules that are&nbsp;too large to penetrate your skin. They sit on the surface, give you a temporary glow, then evaporate by morning.</span></p>",
        "ggsDqyHirza_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>“I’ve been waking up to creases in my skin a lot more lately and it’s affecting my confidence</i></span><br><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>Trying the bio-collagen mask from Nifora gave my skin that plump lift I’ve been meaning to get back. Friends thought I got work done even when I didn’t!! Even the hubby mentioned that I look more glowing lately and I love how I look so good even without makeup on!”</i></span></p>",
        "gguUcZqvrQb_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Words From Our Participants</span></p>",
        "ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Lasting hydration</strong> that didn't fade after 24 hours.</span></p>",
        "ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_1": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Visible plumpness</strong> that smoothened skin and&nbsp;</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">reduced the appearance of wrinkles &amp; fine lines</span></p>",
        "ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_2": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Improved skin texture</strong> that friends and family noticed</span></p>",
        "ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_3": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Zero irritation</strong> even on sensitive, reactive skin</span></p>",
        "ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_4": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Confidence to go makeup-free</strong> all week long</span></p>",
        "ggvmAoWsjGX_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(252, 248, 218, 0.04);\">Before</span></p>",
        "ggvo7LBh3my_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_0a8af824-b65b-4bac-a023-6a6fffe74137.png",
        "ggxJLy4nKfr_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Nifora's Bio-Collagen Mask outperformed every brand we tested across all key metrics: duration of results, depth of hydration, and gentleness on mature skin.</span></p>",
        "ggxW7IXTyUH_text": "<span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.77);\">Results That Lasts Up To 7 Days</span>",
        "ggxrI10l6ZB_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">That's exactly why we partnered with 10 participants between ages 37 – 67 to test the Top 1 mask, Nifora Bio-Collagen.&nbsp;</span></p>",
        "ggzaP1RDbja_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/5_d631cf70-63f9-4696-af7c-c6c0fa922c79.png?v=1770022988"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-626145270316466739"
    },
    "gp_section_626145270333178419": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "78f8663b25b64d2fd7552adde6c29753e6b4d19941c78e3dd4b24d4866acac93_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg1I25rv2az_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">As a Cosmetic Dermatologist for the past 15 years, I’ve seen women in their 30s, 40s, 50s, and even 60s &nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:20px;\"><strong>waste money on masks that burn their skin, tear apart in their hands, or fade within 24 hours.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">You buy expensive serums, drink your water, book facials and try collagen masks but nothing sticks. And it's not your fault.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">That's why my team and I spent the last 6 months &nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:20px;\"><strong>testing 21 of the most popular collagen masks: The viral TikTok ones, the expensive luxury brands, and the budget-friendly options</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">. &nbsp;And the results weren’t what we expected.</span></p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Dr. Nicole Miller | Last Updated: Jan 2026</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "<span style=\"font-size:36px;\">Top Dermatologist:&nbsp;</span><br><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">I Tested 21 Collagen Masks On Women Over 40</span>",
        "ggZHuYgoc8x_text": "After Testing All 21 Collagen Masks,&nbsp;<br>Here's What We Found:",
        "ggcR3JyeIBy_text": "<p>Only 1 Delivered Results That Lasted A Full Week (And Why The #1 Mask Isn't What You'd Expect).</p>",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/hf_20260120_231401_a99bca04-45e6-483e-8a8c-3f92692448e7.png",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/hf_20260120_231401_a99bca04-45e6-483e-8a8c-3f92692448e7.png",
        "gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/hf_20260120_231401_a99bca04-45e6-483e-8a8c-3f92692448e7.png",
        "ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/418ec590-74d5-413b-a8ee-0cf4f039fd0e.jpg",
        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(242, 255, 5, 0.77);color:#000000;\"><strong>Out of the 21 that were tested, only 5 stood out.</strong></span></p><p><br>And the Number 1 among the 5 wasn't the most expensive or the most hyped, scoring a 4.8 out of 5 while the second-place mask only hit 4.1. It delivered results that lasted 7 days from a single use, while bigger brands faded in 1-2 days.</p><p><br>If you're confused about ingredients, worried about reactions, or tired of products that promise results without any proof, this is for you.</p>"
      },
